						               													<description>Konik Morrski is a game based on the history of the 2M3D RPG campaign, which Micha&amp;#197;&amp;#130; &amp;quot;Baniak&amp;quot; Ba&amp;#197;&amp;#132;ka ran on his channel for years.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Konik Morrski is a card game consisting of 26 pairs and two single cards. We give players all the cards. They cannot change their order. On his turn, the player can place a pair in front of him and activate it. Then he draws one card from another player and if he has completed another pair, he can also put it out and activate it. At activation, each pair provides a special skill and provides victory points at the end of the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when there are fewer cards left in the hands than the number of players. If there is someone left with the Konik Morrski card, that player automatically loses without counting points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player with the most points wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
